data.description: Motivated sellers~Price Improvement!!!Welcome to 2217 Alice Kay Dr., a magnificent, well-maintained, two-story home in Iroquois Estates that has been tastefully remodeled. With over 3,000 finished sq. feet, this house is stunning, and the area is wonderful, private, yet close to everything!  Situated on a large lot, this home features four bedrooms, including choice of first or second floor master suites, three fully renovated bathrooms, and a two-car attached garage. You'll notice the gorgeous staircase, neutral interior, and refinished flooring as soon as you walk in the foyer. The living area is large and features a beautiful gas fireplace with built in bookcases and a mantle . The spacious dining room and formal living room  and a first floor master, currently being used as a playroom The spacious eat-in kitchen features newer cabinetry, granite countertops, an updated backsplash, and updated Samsung appliances.  Three bedrooms located on the second floor including  the current master with en suite bath, separate shower and a full walk in closet.  The carpeted basement is ready for your finishing touches, is partially finished, has another full room/office with full bath in basement.  Tons of storage on the other half or finish the rest for a fully finished entertainment space.  Laundry in basement.  Fully fenced in back yard, and detached 2 car garage complete this lovely home.  Call for a private showing today, will not last long!
